Because we gave our environment a .local top level domain(TLD), an error is indicated during installation.  Valid top level domains are domains like .com, .gov, .edu, .net.  Because this is an internal domain, we will leave it as is.  
The naming of local domains is the subject of many debates among systems administrators.
